     Opportunities exist for collaboration with JPL's High Performance
     Computing Group. These range from full-time hiring as a JPL
     employee, to post-doctoral and visiting faculty positions, to co-op
     and summer student positions. Other technical collaborations are
     possible. Please contact Dr. Tom Cwik for further information.
